des:
Get all the latest news, scores and details on upcoming events for the Salem University Tigers.

Competing in NCAA Division II, the Salem Tigers have long enjoyed a strong reputation in intercollegiate athletics. 
 By enabling and invoking this skill, you can keep pace with the Tigers by receiving real time updates of the latest scores, news, and upcoming events.

Established in 1888 as Salem College, Salem University has a 130 year tradition of academic excellence and innovation. The beautiful 100-acre campus is nestled in the Appalachian mountains of West Virginia and hosts students from across the US and from over 40 countries.
